UC71_1 ..> UC71_4 : <<extend>>
UC71_5 ..> UC71_6 : <<include>>
UC71_5 ..> UC71_7 : <<extend>>

UC72_1 ..> UC72_2 : <<extend>>
UC72_1 ..> UC72_3 : <<extend>>
UC72_4 ..> UC72_5 : <<include>>
UC72_7 ..> UC72_6 : <<include>>
UC72_7 ..> UC72_8 : <<include>>
UC72_8 ..> UC72_9 : <<include>>
UC72_7 ..> UC72_10 : <<extend>>
UC72_7 ..> UC72_11 : <<include>>

UC73_1 ..> UC73_2 : <<extend>>
UC73_1 ..> UC73_3 : <<extend>>
UC73_1 ..> UC73_6 : <<extend>>
UC73_1 ..> UC73_7 : <<extend>>

' ===========================
' NOTES
' ===========================
note right of UC70_10
  Kiem tra tuong tac
  thuoc nguy hiem
end note

note right of UC72_8
  Transaction
  Dam bao ton kho
  luon chinh xac
end note

@enduml
